Package meka.filters.multilabel

Class SuperNodeFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.filters.Filter
      • weka.filters.SimpleFilter
        • weka.filters.SimpleBatchFilter
          • meka.filters.multilabel.SuperNodeFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class SuperNodeFilter
extends weka.filters.SimpleBatchFilter
    SuperNodeFilter.java - Super Class Filter. Input:
    Data with label attributes, e.g., [0,1,2,3,4]
    A desired partition of indices, e.g., [[1,3],[4],[0,2]], filter
    Output:
    New data with label attributes: [1+3,4,0+2]
    (the values each attribute can take are pruned if necessary)
    Version:
    June 2012
    Author:
    Jesse Read
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
